<sup>1</sup> Attack rates for influenza-like illness calculated for susceptible members in the control arm who were exposed and unexposed to each characteristic at baseline. Attack rate ratios and confidence intervals generated using log binomial regression models, with generalized estimating equations to account for clustering among household members.</p></fn><fn id="t004fn002"><p>
